with my parents?

45:52.951 --> 45:54.851
- No, I just want to do
what's right for our family.

45:54.853 --> 45:57.487
- Mr. Noah?
- Please, just call me noah!

45:57.489 --> 46:00.289
- There is a visitor for you.

46:13.237 --> 46:15.238
