46:15.240 --> 46:17.240
- Hey hey, there he is.

46:17.242 --> 46:18.775
You dropped your aaa card.

46:18.777 --> 46:20.376
- Oh, thanks man.
- Helen, hey.

46:20.378 --> 46:22.178
Nice to see you again.
You probably don't recognize me.

46:22.180 --> 46:24.447
I've changed a lot.

46:24.449 --> 46:26.983
- I ran into oscar
waiting for the mechanic.

46:26.985 --> 46:28.384
- Yeah, I keep telling the town
they've got to do something

46:28.386 --> 46:30.119
About those potholes out
in ditch plains

46:30.121 --> 46:31.254
And they're, like,
do famous people live there?

46:31.256 --> 46:33.122
No?
Then who cares?

46:33.124 --> 46:34.991
- Ditch plains?
- Yeah.

46:34.993 --> 46:36.259
- Thanks for stopping by, man.

46:36.261 --> 46:38.161
That's great.
Really appreciate that.

46:38.163 --> 46:39.462
We've got something
going on, so...

46:39.464 --> 46:41.164
- Oh, hey,
are bruce and margaret here?

46:41.166 --> 46:42.999
I want to say hey
from my mom and dad,

46:43.001 --> 46:44.400
